## ❌ Violations Found

### 1. CTA: "Get Started" → Should be "Request Beta Access" or "See Enorve Work"

**29 instances** across the site. "Get Started" implies a self-serve product. For a pre-launch beta, this is misleading.

| File | Lines |
|---|---|
| [Navbar.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/components/Navbar.tsx) | 224, 299 |
| [CTASection.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/components/sections/CTASection.tsx) | 37 |
| [MidPageCTA.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/components/sections/MidPageCTA.tsx) | 23 |
| [Pricing.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/pages/Pricing.tsx) | 34, 57, 81, 650 |
| [Contact.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/pages/company/Contact.tsx) | 159, 232 |
| [ROICalculator.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/pages/ROICalculator.tsx) | 202 |
| All 5 product pages | Hero + bottom CTA in each |
| All 4 solution pages | Hero + bottom CTA in each |

---

### 2. "AI-Powered" Label — Sounds Like Intercom

**9 instances.** This is exactly the framing to avoid. "AI-Powered" positions AI as an add-on to a human-operated tool.

| File | Line | Current Text | Suggested Fix |
|---|---|---|---|
| [Home.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/pages/Home.tsx) | 17 | `"AI-Powered Customer Support Platform"` | `"Autonomous Customer Support Platform"` |
| [usePageTitle.ts](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/hooks/usePageTitle.ts) | 25 | `"Enorve - AI-Powered Customer Support Platform"` | `"Enorve - Autonomous Customer Support"` |
| [useStructuredData.ts](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/hooks/useStructuredData.ts) | 37 | `"AI-Powered Customer Support Platform..."` | `"Autonomous support platform..."` |
| [CopilotSection.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/components/sections/CopilotSection.tsx) | 56 | Badge: `"AI-Powered"` | `"Autonomous"` or `"AI-Native"` |
| [CustomerSupport.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/pages/solutions/CustomerSupport.tsx) | 80 | `"AI-Powered Solutions"` | `"Autonomous Support Solutions"` |
| [KnowledgeBase.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/pages/product/KnowledgeBase.tsx) | 57, 411 | `"AI-Powered Help Center"` / badge | `"Self-Resolving Help Center"` |
| [Automation.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/pages/product/Automation.tsx) | 132 | `"AI-Powered Signals"` | `"Autonomous Signals"` |
| [SaaS.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/pages/solutions/SaaS.tsx) | 442 | Badge: `"AI-Powered"` | `"AI-Native"` |

