### 4. "Join hundreds of teams" — False Social Proof

**3 instances** (including TestimonialsSection). Pre-launch product has no customers.

| File | Line | Suggested Fix |
|---|---|---|
| [CTASection.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/components/sections/CTASection.tsx) | 29 | → "See how autonomous support works — from first message to resolution." |
| [MidPageCTA.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/components/sections/MidPageCTA.tsx) | 16 | → "See how AI resolves conversations end-to-end, without human intervention." |
| [TestimonialsSection.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/components/sections/TestimonialsSection.tsx) | 50 | → Remove or reframe entirely |

