### 5. Agent-Centric Framing — "Your agents, supercharged"

The [CopilotSection](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/components/sections/CopilotSection.tsx) and [Features.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/components/Features.tsx) frame AI as a tool for human agents, inverting the philosophy.

| File | Issue | Suggested Fix |
|---|---|---|
| CopilotSection headline | "Your agents, supercharged." | → "When AI escalates, your team is ready." |
| CopilotSection body | "The AI Copilot sits alongside your agents..." | → "When conversations require human judgment, Copilot equips your team with full context, suggested actions, and real-time sentiment — so they resolve faster." |
| CopilotSection badge | "AI-Powered" | → "Human Oversight" |
| Features.tsx heading | "Everything you need. All in one place." | → "Support that runs itself. With everything you need to stay in control." |
| Features.tsx sub | "Powerful tools designed for modern support teams." | → "AI resolves. Humans govern. Every tool built for that." |
| Features.tsx: AI Copilot desc | "Smart suggestions that help agents resolve tickets 2x faster." | → "Real-time context and actions for the moments humans step in." |
| Features.tsx: Auto-Resolution desc | "Let AI handle routine queries while you focus on VIPs." | → "AI resolves autonomously. Humans intervene by exception." |

---

### 6. InboxSection — Human-Operator Framing

[InboxSection.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/components/sections/InboxSection.tsx): "Stop switching between tabs... Your team sees every conversation" frames the inbox as a tool humans operate, not supervise.

| Issue | Suggested Fix |
|---|---|
| Body text: "Your team sees every conversation in one place" | → "AI handles every conversation in one place — your team sees only what needs attention." |
| Feature: "Bulk actions for efficient ticket management" | → "Bulk overrides when human judgment is needed" |

---

### 7. AnalyticsSection — Neutral but Misses Opportunity

[AnalyticsSection.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Jarvis/Documents/Enorve-Market/src/components/sections/AnalyticsSection.tsx): "Data-driven decisions" is neutral. Metric "Active Agents: 24" frames agents as the main workforce.

| Issue | Suggested Fix |
|---|---|
| Headline "Data-driven decisions" | → "See what AI resolved. See where humans were needed." |
| Metric "Active Agents: 24" | → "Human Interventions: 8" (shows AI handles the rest) |
| Metric "AI Automation Rate: 65%" | → "AI Resolution Rate: 65%" |
| Body text | → "Track AI resolution rates, human intervention frequency, and escalation patterns — all in real time." |

