## Summary: Scale of Changes

| Category | Count | Severity |
|---|---|---|
| "Get Started" CTAs | 29 | 🔴 High — false promise for pre-launch |
| "AI-Powered" labels | 9 | 🔴 High — Intercom language |
| "Ready to transform" headlines | 3 | 🟡 Medium — generic |
| "Join hundreds" social proof | 3 | 🔴 High — false claims |
| Agent-centric framing | 5+ sections | 🟡 Medium — inverts the philosophy |
| SEO metadata | 3 files | 🟡 Medium — wrong positioning |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The homepage sections built recently (GovernedAutonomy, AIEngine, Platform, Isometric) are excellently aligned. The violations are concentrated in **older shared components** (CTAs, Navbar, Features, Copilot) and **all product/solution detail pages** which were likely written before the philosophy crystallized.
